body:
GOT ENDING

Okay so here is MY PERFECT ending to game of thrones and what I THINK will actually happen.

MY PERFECT ENDING:

•There will be a finale battle between the living and the dead. Winterfell was taken my the night kings probs.

•During the finale battle it’ll be jon vs night king. He’ll tell daenerys to “dracarys” the both of them and lit every dead fucker up. She’ll cry and be like “eh I love😭 but I’m imma do it”

•Jon will walk out the fire unscathed cause he’s a Targaryen. ( I know he got burnt before but he did die and come back so I think after coming back he came back some magical shit happened to him )

• Jon and Daenerys will marry and have babies and rule the seven kingdoms as equals.

•Sansa will be Queen in the north or lady of winterfell if Jon is still referred to as king. And she will rule it.

•I would love for her and Sandor to get together and have beautiful tall ginger children. But I’ll be alright If she marries Tyrion again or ends up alone ( and is still a bad bitch if she does end up alone )

•Arya continues to be a killing machine(but turns into a cutie for gendry)

•Cersei dies in childbirth as she gives birth to a dwarf, like Tyrion who “killed” his mother during birth.

•Jamie keeps his oath to catelyn and protects Sansa/becomes her queens guard?

•Daavos is a bad bitch you can’t kill him.

•Drogon has dragon eggs🤷🏼‍♀️(who knows how I just want there to be more dragons)

•Sansa and Arya becomes the power sisters of Westeros(let’s stop putting them against each other, they both cool and smart in their own ways)

REALISTIC ENDING:

•Daenerys dies. Drogon lives. Viserion Lives. They go to Jon. Who lives obvs.

•Jon becomes King, he is unhappy with it but it is his birthright.

•Jon appoints Sansa Queen/lady of winterfell and the north.

•Sansa either marries Tyrion again or ends up alone (at the end of the show anyway)

•Arya continues to drift as an assassin

•she kills a lot of fuckers probs

•Jorah,Daavos,Gendry,Ceresi,Sandor and Jamie’s probs die in the finale battle(cause we all know there will be one)

•Daenerys probs ends up pregnant. She either dies before it’s born or gives birth to it then gets killed by the night king. Jon obvs raises it. It’s probs going to be a boy named Eddard?!

summary:
Chapter Summary: Wild teenage shenanigans ensue when Jon and Daenerys decide to attend Theon's Spring Ball after-party.
Rating:...
body:
The Lone Wolf (Ch: 24)

Chapter Summary: Wild teenage shenanigans ensue when Jon and Daenerys decide to attend Theon’s Spring Ball after-party.

Rating: Mature

Read it on ao3: HERE

(Excerpt:)

The next song was a slow one and more couples began making their way onto the makeshift dance floor as the lights were dimmed.  Jon twirled Daenerys back around, cupping her face tenderly in his hands as he brushed his lips over hers.  Once.  Twice. Three times.  Four.  The sensation sent a tingle down her spine, making her knees weak as his hungry mouth devoured hers over and over again. Hands were everywhere as they swayed together in the darkness, oblivious to everyone else in the room.  In that moment, only she and Jon mattered … or even existed.  

“Jon,” she moaned as his hands trailed down her waist before settling on the delicate curves below.

“Daenerys,” he whispered, her name falling softly from his lips.  “My love.”

summary: Jon: Theon, it's not really about food. It's about family. Not necessarily the one you were born with, but the one we chose....
body:
Jon: Theon, it’s not really about food. It’s about family. Not necessarily the one you were born with, but the one we chose. This one. The people we trust to be part of our lives. The people we care about.

Arya: I’m trying to eat here.

Jon: Arya doesn’t have a sentimental bone in her body. I don’t know what Gendry sees in her.
